{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji29.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给陈寄生的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给陈寄生\"的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年8月29日）寄生先生："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惠书读悉，甚以为慰。先生所从事的学术，因我未曾研究，不能赞一词；唯觉中国的历史学，若不用马克思主义的方法去研究，势将徒费精力，不能有良好结果，此点尚祈注意及之。此复，顺致"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬意！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八月二十九日[1]陈寄生，湖南激浦人，长期担任中学教师，研究过少数民族历史。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":8,"day":29}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":117,"page_end":117},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}